{"tid":1790862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懇請大家一定要參與之後嘅所有和你shop，不合作運動係我地所剩無幾嘅抗爭手段，而人數係決定一切","createTime":"2019-12-20T10:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T06:44:32.000Z","uid":31215,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"fa66e7e07b37bf66c77e3cc70214b7032b405780","tid":1790862,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:09:07.000Z","msg":"大家知而家街頭衝突有幾咁難<br />\n以前半個鐘都唔見狗，而家一衝出去就有便衣<br />\n仲有狗跟蹤、滲透、卧底<br />\n而家練parkour 又拉、整連豬又拉、塞鐵又拉<br />\n拉完後果又金<br />\n今日話老師要釘牌、空姐冇得飛大陸<br />\n手足拉嘅拉、傷嘅傷、流亡嘅流亡、保釋嘅唔可以再俾狗咬、死嘅死<br />\n仲搶埋我地7000萬打官司<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅狀況<br />\n大型街頭衝突難度高、風險大<br />\n輕舉妄動叫人出去開花<br />\n只會搞到手足送頭<br />\n之前唔係冇試過<br />\n<br />\n而家我地最有可能嘅抗爭方法<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不合作運動</span></span><br />\n我地要做一D野，有很強滋擾性同攬炒破壞力，但好難拉同好難告<br />\n和你shop真係最適合<br />\n但而家D和你shop 搞成點?<br />\n得幾十人幾百人喺商場遊街叫口號<br />\n結果俾人白眼、成為狗嘅目標<br />\n同和你唱早期成個中庭都係人差天共地<br />\n咁嘅情況仲期望手足裝修，佢地要承受佢風險好大<br />\n冇出嘅人對唔對得住出左去嘅手足? 對唔對得住出唔到去嘅手足?<br />\n<br />\n80萬人遊行，如果呢80萬走哂去和你shop<br />\n要死邊個商場就死邊個商場，要死咩交通就死咩交通，要攬炒咩就攬炒咩，而狗係好難告你<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以應承我<br />\n唔好懶<br />\n唔好覺得和你shop冇用<br />\n有shop 就去，叫多D人一齊去，shop 爆佢<br />\n14年我見證住9嗚有用，但得一日貨，之後因為D人唔再出而失敗<br />\n19年大家可唔可以唔好再搞死和你shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時不合作運動一定要再進化，要更層出不窮<br />\n可以係和你攞，掉9哂藍店D宣傳品<br />\n和你遊車河，上車唔落車等等<br />\n諗到就討論，可行就吹雞做<br />\n6-8月一週二行每次都有幾萬至十幾萬人<br />\n和你x 可唔可以俾返呢個人數出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一定要堅持落去<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"00b36d68716e8d7e1b363f1cbaf5eda92744aebc","tid":1790862,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53e76fdb31863e4ab7f017873e0849b0737d977d","tid":1790862,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e832a36a5268f6c5e7057bb6268c5f692d69b8a","tid":1790862,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8e01e3327f67829e11f33c14dfc0a07e6cd8d5aa","tid":1790862,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"搞唔搞到落去靠大家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad13faa272e94f3d306f364faae71b947adca15","tid":1790862,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"825a578dedaedf7128bbe0ce9e932b7013200db9","tid":1790862,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f784ce2eb98b6aac9b251b29fffef4736aed8669","tid":1790862,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee10cb1dff194eaa4e029869f